00:25:25.010 --> 00:25:26.150
And that's baseball.

00:25:26.150 --> 00:25:29.305
And what we found is we just
found it just went up and up

00:25:29.305 --> 00:25:30.400
and up and up.

00:25:30.400 --> 00:25:32.400
More talent was always better.

00:25:32.400 --> 00:25:35.000
And so you can start to
understand that there's

00:25:35.000 --> 00:25:41.050
a good in hierarchy when we
