00:25:41.050 --> 00:25:41.810
were behavior.

00:25:41.810 --> 00:25:44.070
We need some types
of [INAUDIBLE].

00:25:44.070 --> 00:25:47.370
I want to ask you another
question is, as you can guess,

00:25:47.370 --> 00:25:49.310
I'm going to tell you
